hooks.prompt:
If stop_hook_active is true, respond {"ok": true}.

Otherwise, read the transcript at transcript_path. If summarize_work was already called, respond {"ok": true}.

If not, decide if the session had meaningful work (code changes, decisions, debugging, research). Skip trivial sessions (brief Q&A, file reads, ask-expert queries, casual chat).

Trivial: {"ok": true}
Meaningful and not logged: {"ok": false, "reason": "Call mcp__plugin_ask-expert_ask-expert__summarize_work with a title and summary of what was accomplished."}
